lead_paragraph: The unlikely figure of Caroline Masson emerged from a crowded leaderboard to clinch a one-stroke victory at the Manulife LPGA Classic in Canada on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: German Masson Earns Upset Victory at Manulife LPGA Classic
